oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc45417eb892697dc1ed2e893c7d775d86b554f","tid":51326,"uid":67065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:27:56.000Z","msg":"其實邏輯上係岩 高仿即係老翻<br />\n講明係假 所以唔係呃人<br />\n但佢賣老翻又係第2條罪姐<br />\n代表告佢詐騙唔入罪 但佢賣老翻唔犯第2條法"},{"pid":"888119f21a3514374b40fcf55a0c8ef86bec4649","tid":51326,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:07:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc81f9de968e4adb92665850ee4232620dacabf2","tid":51326,"uid":66983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"大陸有咩係真？"}]}